016/**
017 * Provides adapters for the Ecore types - {@link EPackage}, {@link EClass}, {@link EStructuralFeature}, {@link EOperation}, ...

021public class CoreActionProviderAdapterFactory extends ActionProviderAdapterFactory {

023        public CoreActionProviderAdapterFactory(Context context) {
024                super(context);

026                registerAdapterFactory(

028                                        CorePackage.Literals.SUBSCRIPTION, 
029                                        ActionProvider.class,

031                                        e -> new SubscriptionActionBuilder(e, context) {

036                                                }
037                                                
038                                        }.asActionProvider()));
